<!-- ============ THREE PILLARS ============ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">What We Focus On</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Technology with a <span class="gradient-text">soul.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">TeamworkCares is built around three commitments: mentorship and education, direct community action, and sustainability in the retail industry itself. Every office participates — this isn't a single donation, it's an ongoing program.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-school"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Mentorship & education</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">15 volunteer mentors matched with students from underserved Pinellas County schools through LunchPals. Weekly one-on-one mentoring builds emotional resilience and confidence. Back-to-school backpack drives support six lower-income schools in Clearwater.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-heart-handshake"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Global community action</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Our Mexico team served 350 tamales and hot coffee to hospital patients and their families. Our Clearwater team assembled care bags for children in need through Pack-A-Snack. We support an animal shelter in Mexico City. Every office engages directly — not just donations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-recycle"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Sustainability in retail</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">We help retailers buy less and sell better. 99.9% inventory accuracy prevents overproduction — the number one driver of waste in fashion. Paperless POS and digital receipting cut down paper waste across 30,000+ terminals worldwide.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

