<!-- ============ FEATURED INITIATIVES ============ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Featured Initiatives</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Where our teams have shown <span class="gradient-text">up.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">A running record of the programs TeamworkCares members have supported — not a one-time press release, an ongoing commitment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-first-aid-kit"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">AFUMED — Ukraine medical relief</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">AFUMED provides essential medical support to Ukrainian soldiers on the front lines. Since 2022, TeamworkCares has helped supply 160 first-aid kits and support 53 military units, funding specialized ambulatory kits developed with military doctors.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-droplet"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Kharkiv medical sphere</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Ongoing support for Kharkiv's medical system, including arterial pressure meters and a microwave oven for a children's regional clinical hospital, an oxygen route and ICU beds for a regional infectious disease hospital, and a biochemical analyzer. Also funded New Year gifts for the children of fallen soldiers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-shoe"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Shoes That Fit</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Partnered with Shoes That Fit to provide over 75 pairs of shoes to a local elementary school, so students could attend class in comfort.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-run"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">BLM Virtual Strides 5K</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">The event that launched TeamworkCares. Over 40 participants from around the world joined a virtual 5K raising money for the United Negro College Fund, which helps African American students attend and graduate from college.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-backpack"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">MyStuffBags</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">A back-to-school charity drive providing new belongings — toys, blankets, clothing, school supplies — to children entering shelters after abuse, neglect, or homelessness. TeamworkCares collected over 100 lbs of donations toward the program.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-paw"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Animal shelter support, Mexico City</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Our Mexico City team provides ongoing support to a local animal shelter, part of the same hands-on approach we bring to every TeamworkCares initiative in the region.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

